Description:
The Mun Hean Group represents an extensive network throughout Asia providing specialised solutions in four key areas; 
1) Power Quality Management; 
2) Power Factor Correction; 
3) Lightning Protection and 
4) Industrial Electrical Solutions. 

The group started from Mun Hean Singapore Pte Ltd which was established in 1981 and has long been the market leaders in industrial electrical marketing with its own MH Protection Relays and MH electrical switchboard instruments. The business has expanded to encompass other electrical solutions in its portfolio. Today, the business involves representing leading manufacturers primarily in Europe, on an exclusive basis to manage specialized projects across Asia. The group comprises of companies in Singapore, Malaysia, Indonesia, Hong Kong, Philippines, Vietnam, Myanmar, Taiwan and China. 

Mun Hean's client-base stretches across a diversity of industries; from power utilities, data centres, government and military installations, hospitals, marine, oil & gas, commercial buildings and manufacturing facilities from semi-conductors to food processing. Over 35 in the industry, Mun Hean boasts a project reference of more than 500,000 installations and applications in landmark projects across Asia. Mun Hean embodies a rich history of electrical engineering excellence with a steadfast adherence to its core value, in Transforming Expertise into Solutions.
